Subject: Re: [VB] Heater Box connecting tubes?

Warning, the plastic tubes are not plastic on the inside. The air temp
coming out of the heater boxes is high enough to melt most plastics. I know,
I've tried it. Use a flexible metal duct and wrap it with fiber-glass
insulation.

Craig

